\par \plain\f0\fs18\cf2 Method used to read a window's size, position and state from storage.
\par 
\par \pard \fi-200 \li200 \plain\f1\fs18\cf2\b procedure\plain\f1\fs18\cf2  ReadWdwState(\plain\f1\fs18\cf2\b var\plain\f1\fs18\cf2  Left, Top, Width, Height,\plain\f2\fs18\cf2  \plain\f1\fs18\cf2 State: Integer); \plain\f1\fs18\cf2\b override\plain\f1\fs18\cf2 ;
